                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": false
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "79a781140f2b45569edd8",
                    "stepText": "Now, substitute the given mass ($!$1.5 \\times 10^5 \\; kg$!$) and speed ($!$30 \\; m/s$!$) into the kinetic energy formula to calculate the initial kinetic energy of the train. Compute the value using the expression.",
